(289, 1, '2014-08-11 07:11:26', '2014-08-11 07:11:26', '<div class="figureTable">\r\n<div class="figure"><span class="highlight">15,968 thousand tonnes</span> CO<sub>2</sub> emitted</div>\r\n<div class="figure clearfix">\r\n<div style="float: left; width: 50%; border-right: 1px solid #FFF;"><span class="highlight" style="font-size: 115%; padding: 0 0 5px 13px; display: block;">SCOPE 1</span> <span class="highlight"><img style="position: relative; top: -7px; margin: 0 2px 0 4px; width: 6px;" src="http://cx-sr2013.local.com/wp-content/themes/cathay/assets/img/bullet_triangle.gif" alt="" />15,913,536 </span><span class="highlight" style="font-family: ''Myriad W01 Regular'';">(99.66%)</span>\r\n<span style="font-size: 130%; padding-left: 13px; display: block;">Aviation Fuel, Fuel\r\nCombustion and Towngas</span></div>\r\n<div style="float: left; width: 50%; padding-left: 5px;"><span class="highlight" style="font-size: 115%; padding: 0 0 5px 13px; display: block;">SCOPE 2</span> <span class="highlight"><img style="position: relative; top: -7px; margin: 0 2px 0 4px; width: 6px;" src="http://cx-sr2013.local.com/wp-content/themes/cathay/assets/img/bullet_triangle.gif" alt="" />54,847 </span><span class="highlight" style="font-family: ''Myriad W01 Regular'';">(0.34%)</span>\r\n<span style="font-size: 130%; padding-left: 13px; display: block;">Electricity and Towngas</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="figure"><span class="highlight">12.9%</span> Available tonne kilometre (ATK) improvement since 1998</div>\r\n<div class="figure"><span class="highlight">19.3%</span> Revenue tonne kilometre (RTK) improvement since 1998</div>\r\n<div class="figure">Aircraft are <span class="highlight">75%</span> more fuel efficient now than those in the 1960s</div>\r\n<div class="figure noborder"><span class="highlight">11,000 tCO<sub>2</sub></span> offset in 2012 by staff and passengers</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Environmental Indicators - Aircraft Operations</h2>\r\n<div class="container-div img