(357, 1, '2014-08-21 04:49:44', '2014-08-21 04:49:44', 'The content and quality of the information in our report is guided by the Global Reporting Initiative (GRI) G3.1 reporting guidelines, which were released in 2011. The report application level is A+, as checked by the GRI.\r\n\r\nIn preparation for the new GRI Version 4 guidelines (G4), we also referred to the requirements of the ‘Core’ option for this report.', 'Statement', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'statement', '', '', '2014-08-25 01:30:46', '2014-08-25 01:30:46', '', 355, 'http://cx-sr2013.local.com/?page_id=357', 1, 'page', '', 0),
