(422, 1, '2014-08-22 10:38:56', '2014-08-22 10:38:56', '<div class="figureTable">\r\n<div class="figure"><span class="highlight">15.47 million tonnes</span> CO<sub>2</sub> emissions from fuel burn</div>\r\n<div class="figure clearfix">\r\n<div style="float: left; width: 50%; border-right: 1px solid #FFF;"><span class="highlight" style="font-size: 115%; padding: 0 0 5px 13px; display: block;">SCOPE 1</span> <span class="highlight"><img style="position: relative; top: -7px; margin: 0 2px 0 4px; width: 6px;" src="http://cx-sr2013.local.com/wp-content/themes/cathay/assets/img/bullet_triangle.gif" alt="" />15,913,517 </span><span class="highlight" style="font-family: ''Myriad W01 Regular'';">(99.66%)</span>\r\n<span style="font-size: 130%; padding-left: 13px; display: block;">Aviation Fuel, Fuel\r\nCombustion and Towngas</span></div>\r\n<div style="float: left; width: 50%; padding-left: 5px;"><span class="highlight" style="font-size: 115%; padding: 0 0 5px 13px; display: block;">SCOPE 2</span> <span class="highlight"><img style="position: relative; top: -7px; margin: 0 2px 0 4px; width: 6px;" src="http://cx-sr2013.local.com/wp-content/themes/cathay/assets/img/bullet_triangle.gif" alt="" />54,842 </span><span class="highlight" style="font-family: ''Myriad W01 Regular'';">(0.34%)</span>\r\n<span style="font-size: 130%; padding-left: 13px; display: block;">Electricity and Towngas</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="figure"><span class="highlight">13.3%</span> CO<sub>2</sub> efficiency improvement in relation to available tonne kilometre (ATK) since 1998</div>\r\n<div class="figure"><span class="highlight">19.1%</span> CO<sub>2</sub> efficiency improvement in relation to revenue tonne kilometre (RTK) since 1998</div>\r\n<div class="figure">Aircraft are <span class="highlight">75%</span> more fuel efficient now than those in the 1960s</div>\r\n<div class="figure noborder"><span class="highlight">11,000 tCO<sub>2</sub></span> offset in 2013 by staff and passengers</div>\r\n<