" target="_blank">GRI and HKEx ESG Table</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Investor Relations Materials', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'investor-relations-materials', '', '', '2014-08-26 11:47:39', '2014-08-26 11:47:39', '', 56, 'http://cx-sr2013.local.com/?page_id=445', 3, 'page', '', 0),
